# Important

## Escape Characters
The follow characters have to be escaped when used in normal text sections:
- "*"
- "["
- "]"
- "$"

## Code Blocks
Code Blocks and Latex blocks must start with a new line and end with a new line.
Whitespaces at the beginning of a line cause parsing to fail

Bad:
         ```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
         ```
Good
```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
```

## Termination

Special characters must be terminated.

Good:
This is **Impotant** text

Bad:
This is **Impotant text

Good:
This is a [[link]] to a page

Bad:
This is a [[link to a page
This is a link]] to a page

